flowchart TD
    U[User Request\nquery + limits + sources] --> CLI[Typer CLI]
    U --> API[FastAPI API]

    CLI --> WM[Workflow Manager]
    API --> WM

    WM --> SC[Source Collector Agent]
    SC --> SA[Source Adapters\nAPI/feed first, scrape fallback]

    SA --> RL[Raw Listings]
    RL --> LE[Listing Extraction Agent]
    LE --> NI[Normalized Items]

    NI --> CR[Comp Research Agent]
    CR --> RA[Resale Adapters]
    RA --> CS[Comparable Sales]

    NI --> MA[Margin Analyst Agent]
    CS --> MA
    MA --> ME[Margin Estimates]

    NI --> RR[Reviewer / Ranker]
    ME --> RR
    CS --> RR
    RR --> OUT[Ranked opportunities\nordered by conservative margin]

    OUT --> CLI_OUT[Rich CLI table]
    OUT --> API_OUT[JSON API response]
